{
  "page": {
    "name": "数据字段编辑",
    "parent": "crm/data_field/list",
    "type": 2,
    "auth": [
      {
        "key": "crm/data_field/create",
        "name": "数据字段新增",
        "query": {
          "id": "empty"
        }
      },
      {
        "key": "crm/data_field/update",
        "name": "数据字段编辑",
        "query": {
          "id": "required"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "container",
    "children": {
      "page-main": {
        "type": "main",
        "className": "p-0",
        "children": {
          "dialog-shell": {
            "type": "container",
            "className": "w-full"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "nodes": {
    "dialog-shell": [
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "value": "form.name",
        "mode": "form",
        "validate": [
          {
            "type": "required",
            "message": "字段名称不能为空。"
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "value": "form.field_key",
        "mode": "form",
        "placeholder": "例如 asset.city、pm.audit_status",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-radio",
        "value": "form.field_type",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": "option.field_type",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[360px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "value": "form.default_value",
        "mode": "form",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-switch",
        "name": "条件字段",
        "value": "form.stat_enabled",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "开启后会把该字段值同步为可查询条件，可用于工作台任务显示、流程判断、脚本计算结果写入后的匹配，也可继续用于统计分析。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "trueValue": true,
          "falseValue": false,
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[6rem]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-radio",
        "name": "条件值类型",
        "value": "form.stat_type",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": "option.stat_type",
        "info": "用于说明该条件字段的值怎么被理解和索引：分类适合标签、来源、T节点等枚举值；数值/金额适合可计算数字；财务适合律师费、回款、支出等会生成财务流水的金额字段；时间适合日期时间；状态适合流程状态；文本适合普通文字。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[360px]",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.stat_enabled",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": true
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "name": "条件分组",
        "value": "form.stat_group",
        "mode": "form",
        "placeholder": "例如 线索、资产、司法、PM、财务",
        "info": "用于把条件字段按业务归类，方便后台筛选和统计展示；不参与任务显示、流程判断或脚本匹配本身。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.stat_enabled",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": true
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-select",
        "name": "财务类型",
        "value": "form.stat_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "model": "crm.NewFinanceTypeModel",
          "labelField": "name",
          "order": "sort asc,id asc",
          "pageSize": 200,
          "searchFields": [
            "code",
            "name"
          ],
          "filters": {
            "status": "1"
          }
        },
        "validate": [
          {
            "type": "required",
            "message": "财务类型不能为空。",
            "when": [
              {
                "path": "form.stat_enabled",
                "operator": "equals",
                "value": true
              },
              {
                "path": "form.stat_type",
                "operator": "equals",
                "value": "finance"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "placeholder": "选择生成流水时使用的财务类型",
          "hiddenCondition": "any",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.stat_enabled",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": true
            },
            {
              "path": "form.stat_type",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": "finance"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-array",
        "name": "可选项",
        "value": "form.options",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "维护单选、多选、下拉、多选下拉字段的可选项。选项值是流程判断、任务显示条件、AI填写和自动决策匹配时使用的真实值，建议使用稳定编码，例如 t1、t2、approved。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "pageRoute": "/crm/data_field_option/update",
          "addText": "添加选项",
          "drag": "sort",
          "hiddenCondition": "all",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.field_type",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": "radio"
            },
            {
              "path": "form.field_type",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": "checkbox"
            },
            {
              "path": "form.field_type",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": "select"
            },
            {
              "path": "form.field_type",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": "multi_select"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "form": {
      "id": "",
      "name": "",
      "field_key": "",
      "field_type": "text",
      "default_value": "",
      "stat_enabled": false,
      "stat_type": "dimension",
      "stat_id": "",
      "stat_group": "",
      "options": [],
      "status": 1,
      "sort": 100
    }
  },
  "state": {},
  "action": {
    "submit": {
      "type": "save",
      "params": "form",
      "before": {
        "service": "crm.setting.CrmHook.BeforeSaveDataField"
      }
    }
  }
}
